          "params": [
            {
              "name": "options",
              "type": "TileMapViewOptions",
              "optional": true
            }
          ],
          "returnType": "TileMapView",
          "description": "Create a new TileMapView that groups this map's layers into independently placeable band / layer scene nodes for interleaving application actors between tile layers. Each call returns a fresh, independent view — the map does **not** cache a single global view, so multiple coexisting views of the same map are allowed. The view references this map but never owns it: destroying the view frees only its generated layer/band nodes — never the map, its layers, tileset textures, or any application actors."
        },
